    {
      "id": "PopularPost202327",
      "post_content": "A [steel wall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=steel wall) is a 0/4, while this is a 1/3... hmm... I usually prefer a bit of power over toughness, but if I'm running walls (or wall like creatures), I usually am using their high toughness for a reason... hmm.... I guess it's an okay card mechanically....  \n  \nToo bad I'd never play it solely because the art freaks me out. I don't know what I did to make this brass man mad, but I'll make sure never to repeat it.",
      "posted_by": "Asmodi0000",
